    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis benefits from preventative subframe reinforcement and a recently recalibrated VANOS system, ensuring the variable valve timing operates within factory spec. Power is delivered through the original M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust with documented rod bearing inspections. A visceral, analog performance machine optimized for the twisties.",
