      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and comfort without the showroom price tag. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, though I want to be transparent about a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All tech features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and backup camera, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is solid\u2014the engine idles quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. It has been serviced regularly, with a fresh oil change and a recent tire rotation just completed. This is a well-loved, honest car that is ready for the road today.",
